name: Uranians
overview: Uranians is a space themed shooter game for the BBC Microcomputer and Acorn Electron. It was developed by S Howitt and published by Bug-Byte. Gameplay: Uranians is a fixed shooter. The Uranians, from the planet Uranus, are attacking! Destroy them, but be aware of the missiles they drop. A very big mothership flies at the top and sometimes drops a very big missile that will burst into flames upon impact.
